{"tid":1492840,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜裙子太短「只夠蓋住屁股」！邪惡視角狙擊蜜大腿 網看呆：不許這麼撩","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:16:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":21,"dislike":132,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"689b02dc3fd8b4d194a873e621902f7c7d62045b","tid":1492840,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE中子瑜長得甜美、身材高挑，雖然在隊內年紀小，卻是「最長身」，一雙長腿總會讓人看得目不轉睛，特別是近期在巡迴演唱會上，成年後的子瑜更加散發自信，而長期運動保持的身材更是展現令人羨慕的曲線美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/d4318581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2Fd4318581.jpg&h=a8e239a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜的裙子超短，再加上大長腿，裙長大概只夠剛好蓋住屁股。（圖／翻攝自微博／WithYu周子瑜中文首站）<br />\n<br />\n子瑜從出道之後在身材管理方面相當認真，就算跑了一天的行程回到家也會看影片做運動，意志力讓團員很佩服。作為TWICE隊內的身材擔當，子瑜的體態自然不在話下，優越的身高為她帶來絕佳身材比例，每次舞台表演所穿的短裙都能展現一雙又長又直的美腿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/d4318579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2Fd4318579.jpg&h=a4beedc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜螞蟻腰、大長腿。（圖／翻攝自微博／WithYu周子瑜中文首站）<br />\n<br />\n除了腿之外，螞蟻腰也不容忽視，子瑜近期跟著團員馬不停蹄在世界各地舉辦巡迴演唱會，其中一套黑色T恤搭配螢光粉百褶短裙的服裝讓人印象深刻，上半身略為寬鬆的衣服，下擺收進裙子，短裙腰圍部分貼合腰身，正好勾勒出她的纖腰，另一套中空裝螞蟻腰尤為明顯，被粉絲戲稱是「沒有內臟的細」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/d4318582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2Fd4318582.jpg&h=266d3e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜裙子太短，一坐下差點曝光。（圖／翻攝自微博／WithYu周子瑜中文首站）<br />\n<br />\n只是長期以來南韓女團表演時所穿的裙子長度經常讓粉絲很擔心，子瑜的螢光粉短裙也是，或許因為身高的關係，裙子穿在身上硬是比其他成員顯得短，一坐下黑色安全褲微微露出，讓粉絲看得很擔心，深怕一個不小心就走光，有粉絲以媽媽自稱大呼：「周子瑜，媽媽不許你這麼撩，這腿長我哭了。」"},{"pid":"2f3d0dd78bed227fec1c7006e4704332d7b7de78","tid":1492840,"uid":205928,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"周=周 now<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆射。。"},{"pid":"a967f0c4a2e23f8d6ea40246f2f7155cada491f7","tid":1492840,"uid":74065,"like":73,"dislike":59,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d16e0db98792f66b25e47c19aaaaf900_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-d16e0db98792f66b25e47c19aaaaf900_hd.jpg&h=90210c60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce62cafe9d9af2d3109c7c122a03adcf4a04dc68","tid":1492840,"uid":4391,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"咪撚癲啦台粉"},{"pid":"e33a3a7ba36ea910df629cfe5b9ef25e0b5e6daf","tid":1492840,"uid":46435,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"好想奶她的腿奶到射.."},{"pid":"7b3de33b86c4eb3d786b1b8742c170e4e06af8d4","tid":1492840,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:48.000Z","msg":"摸牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76f3c88c76824d856c0ea2a63f7f27df3107d59","tid":1492840,"uid":63588,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a967f0c4a2e23f8d6ea40246f2f7155cada491f7","tid":1492840,"uid":74065,"like":73,"dislike":59,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d16e0db98792f66b25e47c19aaaaf900_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-d16e0db98792f66b25e47c19aaaaf900_hd.jpg&h=90210c60&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"咪煩啦"},{"pid":"7acece0703e8c94418494a5c898d7d33c725984a","tid":1492840,"uid":40272,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"4f4ddf5dee24b8be783b4d8949ece2a92595a79d","tid":1492840,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":25,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"h